<h3 id="mcetoc_1jkudj88eeq">Build</h3>
<p class="msg msg--info"><em>What did you make, and what key decisions did you make while building?</em></p>
<p>I used scratch to build this. I used variables to handle the interaction and define blocks to manage the simpleness.</p>
<p>I am particularly proud of bob.</p>
<hr>
